To disable mouse-acceleration add the file in xorg.conf.d folder to /etc/X11/

To change the mouse speed without acceleration, simply use libinput, by installing xinput.

xinput list // to find device id.
xinput set-prop 8 "Coordinate Transformation Matrix" 2.2 0 0 0 2.2 0 0 0 1 // labba med 2.2 och 2.2...

